   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="HS00048772X_0028"/>Herrn Gu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tav Schwarzkopf</addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb51">Wien I</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb207301">Tiefer Graben 17</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="HS00048772X_0027"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb245"><hi rend="pre-print">Hotel Esplanade, Berlin</hi></rs></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="HS00048772X_0028"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>15. 3. 25</date> </dateline></opener><p>Am <date>14.</date> war hier <rs type="event" ref="#pmb353205" subtype="implied">Première</rs> des <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29823">Märchen</rs> (am <rs type="org" ref="#pmb35053">Lessingtheater</rs>) – 32 Jahre nach <rs type="event" ref="#pmb35068" subtype="implied"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></rs>. Ich sah mir am gleichen Abend <rs type="event" ref="#pmb210331" subtype="implied"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb81419">Charleys Tante</rs></rs> an <del rend="strikethrough"><unclear>mit</unclear></del> mit Heini<!-- nicht indizieren, ist Autor des Briefes --> als <rs type="work" ref="#pmb81419" subtype="implied">Jack</rs> (singend und tanzend.) Wer mir das am
                  <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04362-1"/><date>1. Dezember 1893</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04362-1">Dem Tag der <rs type="event" ref="#pmb35068">Uraufführung</rs> am <rs type="org" ref="#pmb36430">Deutschen
                     Volkstheater</rs> in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs>.</note>
               prophezeiht hätte. <date>Heute</date> trat  <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12692">Heini</rs> zum 500. Mal auf! –</p><closer>Herzliche Grüße. Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="2"><p><handShift scribe="#pmb12692"/>Viele herzliche Grüße</p><closer><signed>Heini.</signed></closer></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="2"><p><handShift scribe="#pmb21647"/>Mit be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ten Empfehlungen Ihr</p><closer><signed>PaulMarx</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
